name: HIRO_V
description:
Hiro_V is part of the Searching For Hiroshige series that takes inspiration traditional Japanese woodblock printing. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3531x5200px PNG [bitmap image] 1/1
